15. Miscellaneous
When we mention Grill’d in this policy, we mean all the companies in the Grill’d Group including Grill’d Pty Ltd (ACN 106 297 394), Grill’d Franchising Pty Ltd (ACN 116 019 231), Grill’d IP Pty Ltd (ACN 116 019 213), Grill’d Leasing Pty Ltd (ACN 116 019 259), each Grill’d franchisee and all of our other related companies.
Sometimes, things change, and we may need to update this Privacy Policy. Grill’d may do this at any time without direct notice to you and you can find the most recent version on the Grill’d Website.
